text: Dekatriata is a clade of chelicerates, it is made up of Arachnida (Spiders, scorpions, mites, and their relatives), Chasmataspidida (extinct chelicerate group), Eurypterida (Sea Scorpions), as well as genuses of Winneshiekia and Houia. == References == Category:Arachnids Category:Chelicerata
title: Dekatriata
